entries.abort: We are going to be at the mercy of our enemies without you. Your commander will hear of this failure.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning system for disabled recon vessel.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Vessel's location sent to your nav computer. Assist the vessel with repairs and escort it to safety.
entries.complete: Good work, pilot. The recon ship has been returned safely.
entries.docking_complete: Repairs completed. Prepare to follow the recon shuttle to a safe jump location.
entries.failed_destroy: You were ordered to get that ship back to us in one piece. If you are unable to handle your assignments perhaps you should retire.
entries.panic_1: Those are the same fighters that hit me earlier.
entries.panic_2: I saw a massive number of those same ships just before I was attacked.
entries.panic_3: Looks like the same Coynite's that hit me earlier.
entries.panic_4: They really don't want me to report back about what I discovered.
entries.panic_5: I saw a massive number of those same ships just before I was attacked.
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the shuttle and assist it with any repairs it might need.
entries.quest_dock_t: Assist the Recon Shuttle with Repairs
entries.quest_escort_d: Follow and protect the shuttle as it moves through the Dathomir system.
entries.quest_location_d: The distress signal is coming from inside the Dathomir system. A navigation waypoint to its location will be supplied to you.
entries.recovery_success: Good job, pilot. You are really making a name for yourself.
entries.rescue_abandoned: We are going to be at the mercy of our enemies without you. Your commander will hear of this failure.
entries.rescue_phase_1: Good to see a friendly out here.
entries.rescue_phase_2: Engines back online. We will be underway shortly.

entries.taunt_1: We are back to finish the job.
entries.taunt_2: This is going to be too easy. Where is the challenge?
entries.taunt_3: My brothers and I shall sings songs of your demise.
entries.taunt_5: What? How dare you! That's it! Time to be vaporized.
entries.thanks_1: Good to have you on our side. I will report on the massing of Coynite mercs in the region to our superiors.

entries.title: Dathomir System: Rescue the Recon Shuttle
entries.title_d: A distress signal has gone out from a recon shuttle. Apparently the Coynite mercenaries that attacked you also attacked this other vessel. The shuttle is damaged but still functional. The Coynite apparently broke off their attack on it in order to rescue the smuggler you captured. Assist the shuttle and escort it to safety.
